results.name: Inverse binomial transform of A156616.
link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..3000
formula: G.f.: (1/(1 + x))*exp(Sum_{k>=1} (sigma_2(2*k) - sigma_2(k))*x^k/(2*k*(1 + x)^k)). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Oct 15 2018
mathematica: nmax = 40; s = CoefficientList[Series[Product[((1+x^k)/(1-x^k))^k, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]; Table[Sum[(-1)^(n-k) * Binomial[n, k] * s[[k+1]], {k, 0, n}], {n, 0, nmax}]
